immersiveengineering.optifinePoseStackWa: Immersive Engineering detected an incompatible version of Optifine. Due to Optifine's patching process, this version of Optifine removes Forge-added methods which are used, directly or indirectly, by Immersive Engineering and many other mods. As a result, you will probably experience a crash at virtually random times, e.g. when a search matches certain items. It is recommended that you do not use Optifine until this is fixed.
